Name: MSP_API_VERSION
Parameters:
Uint8: MSP_Protocol Version
Uint8: API Version Major
Uint8: API Version Minor
Description:
Get API version information
Protocol version is always 0, even when illogical

Parameters:
uint8: FC Version Major

Uint8[4]: Board Identifier
uint16: Hardware Revision Number

Name: MSP_INAV_PID
Parameters:
uint8: aysnc mode
Uint16 : Acc Task Frequency
Uint16: attitude Task Frequency
Uint8 : Heading Hold Rate Limit
Uint8:  Heading Hold Error LPF freq
Uint16: Yaw jump prevention limit
Uint8: Gyro LPF
Uint8:  Acc soft LPF hz
Uint8[4]: reserved (set to 0)

Name: MSP_SET_INAV_PID
Parameters:
uint8: aysnc mode
Uint16 : Acc Task Frequency
Uint16: attitude Task Frequency
Uint8 : Heading Hold Rate Limit
Uint8:  Unused (aka Heading Hold Error LPF freq)
Uint16: Yaw jump prevention limit
Uint8: Gyro LPF
Uint8:  Acc soft LPF hz
Uint8[4]: reserved (set to 0)
